# Color Blocks


# Color block range
# The range of colors to print.
#
# Default:  &#x27;0&#x27;, &#x27;15&#x27;
# Values:   &#x27;num&#x27;
# Flag:     --block_range
#
# Example:
#
# Display colors 0-7 in the blocks.  (8 colors)
# neofetch --block_range 0 7
#
# Display colors 0-15 in the blocks. (16 colors)
